      • make

        public static HDateTimeRange make(String str,
                                  HTimeZone tz)
        Parse from string using the given timezone as context for date based ranges. The formats are: - "today" - "yesterday" - "{date}" - "{date},{date}" - "{dateTime},{dateTime}" - "{dateTime}" // anything after given timestamp Throw ParseException is invalid string format.
